<br>
Well actually boots/gloves/arms are insanely common for every slot...then it reverts to the top ranking.<br>
<br>
We've had a lot of plate BPs, one 4 hour camp we got 3.  Silk has been insanely rare however.  We've gotten one silk robe in the past 7 months. <p><font face="arial" size="-1"><a href=mailto:mirithal@hotmail.com>Mirithal Darkbuster 59 Paladin  <b>||</b>  Maepole 43 Warrior</a><br>
