<br>
<br>
Hanka <br>
Level 21 Enchanter <br>
Aventyre Krigare <br>
<br>
Povar <br></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bpaladinsofnorrath.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=lythe>Lythe</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Wandering Knight</span><br>  Posts: 118<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(4/22/02 2:02:06 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=153.topic&index=21>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Drop rates in HoT</span><hr size=1> Plate is by far the most common drop in HoT, which is a good thing, since there are alot more plate using classes.  We seem to get Plate &gt;&gt; Silk ~ Chain &gt; Leather, though I think our shortage is leather/silk. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukidkod1ak.showPublicProfile?language=EN>kidkod1ak</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Blessed Protector</span><br>  Posts: 310<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(4/22/02 4:20:02 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=153.topic&index=22>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Drop rates in HoT</span><hr size=1> Well over the last 4 days we put in about 40 hours in HoT. Here's our totals.<br>
<br>
